org.grobid.core.layout

Class PDFAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grobid.core.layout.PDFAnnotation

  • public class PDFAnnotation
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for representing an annotation present in a PDF source file. Annotations are area in the PDF document associated with an action (URI for external web link, goto for internal document link).
